                Mr. Houghton
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-0262fbe0-58a1-4788-af48-b653285b8329" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1952-05-20/debates/f050ec40-abaa-49a3-b1bc-da676aa525d4/Clause31%E2%80%94(ChargeOfTheExcessProfitsLevy)#contribution-0262fbe0-58a1-4788-af48-b653285b8329">
