        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-c16a7c4f-5aae-4632-b4d4-e99cc6bf5320">
                Mr. Nabarro
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-c16a7c4f-5aae-4632-b4d4-e99cc6bf5320" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1952-05-20/debates/f050ec40-abaa-49a3-b1bc-da676aa525d4/Clause31%E2%80%94(ChargeOfTheExcessProfitsLevy)#contribution-c16a7c4f-5aae-4632-b4d4-e99cc6bf5320">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">For years past—ever since 1946, and even earlier—the Inland Revenue have had the greatest difficulty in recruiting staff of the right type. The E.P.L. is reputed to be a temporary tax, lasting for two or three years. Is it not the case that it would take at least a decade to build up the strength of the Inland Revenue staff to a sufficient level to cope with all the numerous complexities which the Excess Profits Levy is bound to bring forward?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-c16a7c4f-5aae-4632-b4d4-e99cc6bf5320" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1952-05-20/debates/f050ec40-abaa-49a3-b1bc-da676aa525d4/Clause31%E2%80%94(ChargeOfTheExcessProfitsLevy)#contribution-c16a7c4f-5aae-4632-b4d4-e99cc6bf5320">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-9647dbb8-aef7-4455-a8a6-972c7e218d5d">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-9647dbb8-aef7-4455-a8a6-972c7e218d5d">
