    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Does not the right hon. Gentleman propose to state any figures? He seems to be passing away from the subject.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-e31b1b92-ca11-4511-a9dd-ff30feeb887f" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1952-05-20/debates/f050ec40-abaa-49a3-b1bc-da676aa525d4/Clause31%E2%80%94(ChargeOfTheExcessProfitsLevy)#contribution-e31b1b92-ca11-4511-a9dd-ff30feeb887f">
