        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-131aeeda-f921-4ff2-aabe-99cdf12ff61b">
                Mr. R. A. Butler
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-131aeeda-f921-4ff2-aabe-99cdf12ff61b" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1952-05-20/debates/f050ec40-abaa-49a3-b1bc-da676aa525d4/Clause31%E2%80%94(ChargeOfTheExcessProfitsLevy)#contribution-131aeeda-f921-4ff2-aabe-99cdf12ff61b">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">The right hon. Gentleman should not try to drive a wedge between myself and the Prime Minister. That is the oldest game in <span id="395" class="column-number" data-column-number="395"></span> politics. The doctrine of Cabinet responsibility applied to the shadow cabinet as much as it applies to the flesh and blood Cabinet of today.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-131aeeda-f921-4ff2-aabe-99cdf12ff61b" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1952-05-20/debates/f050ec40-abaa-49a3-b1bc-da676aa525d4/Clause31%E2%80%94(ChargeOfTheExcessProfitsLevy)#contribution-131aeeda-f921-4ff2-aabe-99cdf12ff61b">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
